{
  "id": "RAW_d02a4e21",
  "title": "Agent「记吃不记打」？华为诺亚&港中文发布 SCOPE：Prompt 自我进化，让 HLE 成功率翻倍",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651009172&idx=2&sn=022ce6551ca84027e6761bf440703ae5",
  "date": "2025-12-26 04:33:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;visibility: visible;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 LLM Agent 领域，有一个常见的问题：Agent 明明 \"看到了\" 错误信息，却总是重蹈覆辙。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当 Agent 遇到工具调用错误时，错误日志里往往已经包含了解决方案 —— 正确的参数格式、有效的 API 用法、甚至是直接可用的替代方案。然而，静态的 Prompt 无法让 Agent 从这些反馈中 “学到教训”，导致它们陷入 “错误循环”：承认失败，却重复同样的动作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">华为诺亚方舟实验室与香港中文大学联合发布的 SCOPE 框架，旨在解决这一问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"503524817\" data-ratio=\"0.1962962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bf1787e1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21TFQngVaoM1oBrygr1O0R9PIuFXXUd0ufutaKUXxpmfBe3wIO7vBjMPw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文：《</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">SCOPE: Prompt Evolution for Enhancing Agent Effectiveness</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">》</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文地址：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.15374\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.15374</a>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">开源地址：<a href=\"https://github.com/JarvisPei/SCOPE\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/JarvisPei/SCOPE</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SCOPE 的核心思想是：既然 Agent 会被反复调用，那么它的 Prompt 就可以在执行过程中不断进化。通过从执行轨迹中自动提炼指导规则，SCOPE 让 Agent 能够 \"从错误中学习\"，并将经验固化到 Prompt 中，实现自我进化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524818\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5187239944521498\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"721\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2aff3c00&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21TZZTbbUbJBBgInVIxO9ibcSRFmbdDszP8yExqCCYabfN2aa0OaG3iaVqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524819\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6806883365200764\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"523\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=72bec674&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21TYKJren6pkjgZzvLicmyhPk3YYZCicTDn2y2Vq8OSeal49Rvq7mB0PxRA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Agent 的两大失败模式</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究团队分析了 GAIA 和 DeepSearch 基准上的 Agent 执行日志，发现了两类典型的失败模式：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">第一类是「纠正型失败」(Corrective Failure)：当错误发生时，执行轨迹中包含明确的信号（错误消息、堆栈跟踪、有效参数列表），本应指导 Agent 进行修正。然而，静态的 Agent 把这些信息当作泛泛的 “警报”，而不是可操作的反馈。研究者观察到大量案例，Agent 在错误消息明确列出正确用法的情况下仍然误用工具，形成 “错误循环”。更严重的情况下，Agent 甚至会为了继续执行而 “编造数据”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">第二类是「增强型失败」(Enhancement Failure)：即使没有明显错误，Agent 也会错过优化机会。比如当搜索结果不理想时，上下文往往暗示可以尝试同义词（如 “base on balls” 与 “walks”），但 Agent 却固守单一关键词策略。这种失败更加隐蔽，但同样影响任务成功率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524820\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.40185185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=67a56f47&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21T6dOTMdRA4RpvO2S2icISUMWAlHwicPxfO1sibCUicgyZlw8cIc2ibAkyRjQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这两类失败的根本原因是相同的：静态 Prompt 缺乏从执行反馈中学习的机制。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">SCOPE 框架：从执行轨迹中学习</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524821\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3907407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=02dab465&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21Tumw8IeUhQkJnPWrSMbKy1zqF4AXrQwd8VMVnicicqOZJDsbkUeTZG7sg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">针对上述问题，SCOPE 将上下文管理从手动工程任务转变为自动优化过程。其核心洞察是：Agent 自身的执行轨迹就是最好的学习信号。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SCOPE 框架由四个核心组件构成：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">1. 指导规则合成（Guideline Synthesis）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当 Agent 遇到错误或完成子任务时，SCOPE 的生成器（Generator）会分析执行轨迹，合成候选指导规则。这里采用 Best-of-N 策略：生成多个候选规则，然后由选择器（Selector）挑选最佳的一条。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">针对不同场景，SCOPE 使用两种合成模式：纠正型合成从错误中提取教训，增强型合成从成功模式中挖掘优化机会。实验表明，增强型规则占所有合成规则的 61%，说明 SCOPE 不仅仅是 “错误修复器”，更是一个主动的优化器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">2. 双流路由机制（Dual-Stream Routing）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">合成的规则并非同等对待。SCOPE 引入分类器（Classifier）将规则路由到两个记忆流：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">战术记忆（Tactical Memory）：存储任务特定的规则，如 “当前数据集的‘Amount’列包含货币符号，计算前需进行清洗”。这些规则仅在当前任务的数据上下文中有效。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">战略记忆（Strategic Memory）：存储跨任务通用的规则，如 “当 Web 搜索返回结果为空时，尝试泛化搜索关键词而不是重复搜索”。这些规则会持久化保存，应用于未来所有任务。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">只有高置信度（阈值设为 0.85）的通用规则才会被提升到战略记忆，避免过拟合到特定任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">3. 记忆优化（Memory Optimization）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">随着规则积累，战略记忆可能包含冗余或冲突的内容。SCOPE 的优化器（Optimizer）会执行三步清理：冲突解决（合并矛盾规则）、冗余剪枝（移除被更通用规则覆盖的具体规则）、整合归并（将相似规则合并为综合性规则）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">4. 视角驱动探索（Perspective-Driven Exploration）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">单一进化路径可能收敛到某种策略，在部分任务上表现较好但在其他任务上失效。为了提高策略覆盖，SCOPE 初始化多个并行流，每个流由不同的 \"视角\" 引导（如效率优先 vs. 周全优先），各自进化出不同的 Prompt。测试时选择最佳结果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">实验结果：HLE 成功率从 14% 提升到 39%</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究团队在三个基准上进行了评估：HLE（2500 道专家级问题）、GAIA 和 DeepSearch。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实验结果表明，SCOPE 在所有基准上都取得了提升：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524822\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5512820512820513\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"780\" style=\"width: 486px;height: 268px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8c0ca84c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21T48NjicRsFmFjcvPrNBdRnxTW0HgIzGqsRr5wcgzbDVXxydeR3kZM5Pw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 HLE 基准上，SCOPE 将任务成功率从 14.23% 提升到 38.64%。在 GAIA 基准上，成功率从 32.73% 提升到 56.97%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为了更准确地表达不同组件的贡献，论文中给出了消融实验。如下图所示，指导规则生成器提供 + 4.85% 的初始提升，双流路由贡献 + 3.63%，Best-of-N 选择贡献 + 3.03%，记忆优化贡献 + 1.82%，而视角驱动探索带来 + 10.91% 的提升。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524823\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3708133971291866\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"836\" style=\"width: 462px;height: 171px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=80cd5efd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21T5BI40NkjgeYsVo6xLQGC4GyrR9O7ibfmJnr9QozdibLmYBWA5p1IYoUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">值得注意的是，在知识密集型领域（如生物 / 医学、化学），SCOPE 的提升较为明显：生物 / 医学从 14.9% 提升到 43.2%，化学从 14.1% 提升到 50.3%。这些领域的问题往往涉及复杂的专业概念和严格的推理流程，SCOPE 合成的领域特定规则能够帮助 Agent 更好地理解和遵循这些要求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524824\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5985130111524164\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"807\" style=\"width: 413px;height: 247px;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/KmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21TQpcWanxIeDPmE23UqgiatcTO3GnAUgia7K6rdRdUuPKmvNZLD9IMNeGw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"807\" data-cropy1=\"11.16955017301038\" data-cropy2=\"494.25259515570934\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=51168186&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21TXdFTEpHNLoKFpzKLpKvtAC8ib93sL5szFkcjxONpHvbcjFhpd6MhJeQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">Agent 真的在 \"听话\" 吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一个关键问题是：合成的规则是否真正影响了 Agent 的行为？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如下图所示，研究团队观察到了 \"语言采纳\" 现象：当 SCOPE 合成了 \"始终列出所有可能的标签同义词和短语变体\" 这一规则后，Agent 后续输出中直接引用了相同的措辞。这表明规则被整合到了 Agent 的决策过程中。此外，行为变化通常在规则合成后几秒内就会发生，展示了单个任务内的实时适应能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524826\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.035143769968051\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"626\" style=\"width: 410px;height: 424px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a3cbb3f8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21TvHzIgDTOfLfes40S2Faj0mom1cSCzfk3nekgkHx7qAYpnpADxafSibg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">视角驱动策略多样性</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">视角驱动探索的设计得到了实验验证。如下图所示，效率流（Efficiency Stream）和周全流（Thoroughness Stream）的总体准确率相近（44.85% vs 46.06%），但两者解决的问题重合度仅为 33.94%，这意味着约 23% 的问题只能被其中一个视角解决。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">效率流在 GAIA 的 Level 3 任务上表现更好（26.92% vs 11.54%），说明精简的上下文管理对复杂长程任务更有效；而周全流在 Level 2 任务上更强。全局集成捕获了两种策略的优势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524827\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.2905263157894737\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"950\" style=\"width: 486px;height: 141px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f34fcc78&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21TOdHppD8pjDVPJISCdIZp3datKLjOClCm76PT3b5oxzWQKLBO5RC78w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">定性分析显示，面对同一个 HTTP 403 访问拒绝错误，效率流学会 “快速失败”—— 立即升级到搜索 Agent，不再重试；而周全流则学会 “寻找替代来源”—— 尝试 Archive.org 或转录工具。这种二元性让 SCOPE 能够同时处理时间紧迫型和深度检索型任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524832\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.701062215477997\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"659\" style=\"width: 444px;height: 311px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b37445dc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21TapQgxlNhWDnHrZkWkrdjAPPsFG0AoGIicUNfzzwXB3Igk5pPyPiaYsTQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">SCOPE 的意义</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">华为诺亚方舟实验室与香港中文大学联合提出的 SCOPE 框架，通过将执行轨迹作为学习信号、将 Prompt 视为可进化的参数，实现了 Agent 的在线自我优化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">与现有方法相比，SCOPE 具有三个主要特点：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">步级别适应（Step-level adaptation）：在执行过程中更新 Prompt，允许从任务中途的失败中恢复，而非等到任务结束才学习。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">单 Agent 优化（Per-agent optimization）：每个 Agent 角色基于自身特定的模式进化 Prompt，而非使用 \"一刀切\" 的策略库。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">主动优化：61% 的规则来自成功模式的增强型合成，而非仅仅修复错误。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503524833\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5009259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=40d5a536&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9vQ5z983QmeJMF0ibtxO21TxNdib9ttSjXNCCJne4WNjSqqgyelJlW9UR2QyJGn6XFtYszbEXq3blw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SCOPE 的代码已在 GitHub 开源。正如论文所总结的：“与其工程化静态 Prompt，不如让 Agent 在线进化自己的 Prompt。” 这一思路可能为下一代 Agent 系统的设计提供新的方向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">值得一提的是，SCOPE 的开源实现具有较好的实用性：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">即插即用：只需在 Agent 执行循环中调用 `on_step_complete ()` 接口，即可为现有 Agent 系统添加自我进化能力，无需修改原有架构。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型无关：通过统一的适配器接口支持 OpenAI、Anthropic 以及 100 + 其他模型提供商（via LiteLLM），方便开发者使用自己偏好的模型。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">轻量部署：核心依赖精简，可通过 `pip install scope-optimizer` 一键安装。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">SCOPE 提供了一套完整的实现框架，其核心洞察是：Agent 的执行轨迹本身就是最好的学习素材 —— 关键在于如何将这些经验有效地编码到 Prompt 中。对于希望增强 Agent 系统效能的开发者而言，SCOPE 提供了一个可直接使用的解决方案。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "华为诺亚方舟实验室与香港中文大学联合发布了 SCOPE 框架，通过 Prompt 自我进化机制，让 LLM Agent 能从执行轨迹中的错误和成功经验中学习，显著提升了 Agent 的任务成功率和适应性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "华为诺亚方舟实验室与香港中文大学联合发布了 SCOPE 框架，通过 Prompt 自我进化机制，让 LLM Agent 能从执行轨迹中的错误和成功经验中学习，显著提升了 Agent 的任务成功率和适应性。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了华为诺亚方舟实验室与香港中文大学联合发布的 SCOPE 框架，旨在解决 LLM Agent 在执行任务时“记吃不记打”的问题，即面对错误信息却无法有效学习和改进。研究团队通过分析发现 Agent 存在“纠正型失败”和“增强型失败”两大模式。SCOPE 框架的核心思想是让 Agent 的 Prompt 在执行过程中通过自动提炼指导规则实现自我进化。该框架包含四大核心组件：指导规则合成（从错误和成功经验中提炼）、双流路由机制（将规则分类为战术记忆和战略记忆）、记忆优化（清理冗余和冲突规则）和视角驱动探索（并行进化以提高策略覆盖）。实验结果显示，SCOPE 在 HLE 基准上的任务成功率从 14.23%提升到 38.64%，在 GAIA 基准上从 32.73%提升到 56.97%，尤其在知识密集型领域提升显著。SCOPE 的意义在于其在线、步级别、单 Agent 以及主动优化的特点，并已开源，提供即插即用、模型无关的轻量级解决方案。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "LLM Agent 在任务执行中存在“纠正型失败”和“增强型失败”两大固有缺陷。",
      "explanation": "Agent 虽能看到错误提示，却因 Prompt 静态性而无法学习纠正，导致反复犯错；即使无明显错误，也常错过优化机会，未能充分利用上下文信息进行策略增强。"
    },
    {
      "point": "SCOPE 框架通过 Prompt 自我进化机制，使 Agent 能从执行轨迹中学习并提升任务成功率。",
      "explanation": "SCOPE 不是依赖静态 Prompt，而是让 Prompt 在 Agent 执行过程中动态生成和进化指导规则，从而实现 Agent 的在线、步级别自我优化。"
    },
    {
      "point": "SCOPE 框架包含指导规则合成、双流路由、记忆优化和视角驱动探索四个核心组件。",
      "explanation": "这些组件协同工作，确保 Agent 能从错误中学习、从成功中优化，并有效管理和利用学习到的经验，同时通过多视角探索避免策略收敛。"
    },
    {
      "point": "实验证明 SCOPE 显著提升了 Agent 在各类基准上的任务成功率，尤其在知识密集型领域效果更优。",
      "explanation": "在 HLE 基准上成功率从 14.23%提升至 38.64%，并能让 Agent 采纳和执行合成的规则，实现行为的实际改变。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "在 LLM Agent 领域，有一个常见的问题：Agent 明明 \"看到了\" 错误信息，却总是重蹈覆辙。",
    "SCOPE 的核心思想是：既然 Agent 会被反复调用，那么它的 Prompt 就可以在执行过程中不断进化。",
    "静态 Prompt 缺乏从执行反馈中学习的机制。",
    "与其工程化静态 Prompt，不如让 Agent 在线进化自己的 Prompt。",
    "SCOPE 的开源实现具有较好的实用性：即插即用、模型无关、轻量部署。"
  ],
